Don't pay more to take advantage of the most comprehensive conference of the year (350+ speakers/panelists) to address the concerns of operating management from operating companies.    
You've seen the advertising and the promotional material and if you have not yet decided to attend, you may wish to view the latest on our web site.  The links below will take you to the section of the program of most interest to you.  You have access to all of these strategic tracks and tactical meetings with your registration fee:  
STRATEGIC TRACKS
 

  
