 Natural Gas Infrastructure Forum  (Just how secure is the price and delivery of this increasingly important fuel?)  
 Nuclear Renaissance Forum  (Is the technology that our industry once claimed would produce power too cheap to meter back?)  
 Alternative Power Forum  (DG, wind, solar, storage - to what extent will they be a part of our future?)  
 e-ProCom  (What is the future of integrating e-Commerce into your activities and what will be the impact?)  
